.****************************************************************************
.*                                OPTN0000                                  *
.*                        get user options or exit                          *
.*                                                                          *
.*    valid options     --->  (0) Exit                                      *
.*                            (1) Add                                       *
.*                            (2) Modify                                    *
.*                            (3) Delete                                    *
